# Sprint 62: Refactoring & Optimization Sprint
# S62.ptl

v:4
role: planner
gate: LOCKED

objective: |
  Comprehensive refactoring and optimization of NaviTrack PWA: eliminate code duplication,
  optimize component architecture, improve performance, implement proper error boundaries,
  consolidate API patterns, optimize bundle size, enhance type safety, and improve developer
  experience with better debugging tools and documentation.

requires: [FRONTEND_DEV, ARCHITECT]
invariants: sprints/53/S53-INVARIANTS.md
design-ref: sprints/56/artifacts/S56-Consolidated-Roadmap.md

